of that flag.

37:29.281 --> 37:30.713
Let's get ahead of this thing.

37:30.715 --> 37:33.248
Hey, can somebody move that?

37:33.250 --> 37:36.718
(sirens wailing)

37:36.720 --> 37:38.419
What?

37:38.421 --> 37:40.320
Use your words.

37:40.322 --> 37:42.388
Jerk.

37:44.325 --> 37:46.358
I'm scared.

37:46.360 --> 37:49.727
That's the first time
I've ever heard you say that.

37:51.297 --> 37:53.297
Happy?

37:53.299 --> 37:55.098
Do you know there's a better
chance of a nuclear apocalypse

37:55.100 --> 37:57.133
than of me ever hurting you?

38:07.378 --> 38:09.444
What do you see?

38:11.381 --> 38:14.882
A rare and delightful fungus.

38:14.884 --> 38:17.918
ADRIANA: <i> The satellite is
being</i> <i> recovered five miles</i>

38:17.920 --> 38:19.386
off the coast of Santa Monica.

